European Stock Futures Decline as German Growth Trails Forecasts on Crisis

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-08-16T06:15:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-16/european-stock-futures-decline-as-german-growth-trails-forecasts-on-crisis.html
European stock-index futures fell as
a report showed the German economy almost stalled in the second
quarter.  Futures on the Euro Stoxx 50 Index expiring in September
dropped 0.6 percent to 2,307 at 7:13 a.m. in  London , having
earlier risen 0.3 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
 arummer@bloomberg.net  